        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Huehhuei cactli tlapohtoc ipan tlalli tlen tlamayanco, nochipa tlachihualli ipan ce tepexitl, zo tlan pan ce calli, ni pano ipan pizo zo itzompac.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
